{% doc %}
  Vendors page body content for MSA static pages.
{% enddoc %}

<div class="section msa-page" style="--section-pt: 20px; --section-pb: 60px;">
  <div class="fluid_container">
    <div class="msa-page__intro">
      <p class="msa-page__eyebrow">Our vendor network</p>
      <h2 class="msa-page__heading">Strategic partnerships for quality and reliability</h2>
      <div class="msa-page__text rte">
        <p>Our technical expertise and extensive industry experience enable us to identify and engage the most suitable vendors for each project, ensuring that the specific requirements of every client are fully met.</p>
        <p>Whether handling small-scale, quick-turnaround orders or managing value-added production involving diverse fabrics, styles, and accessories, we have consistently demonstrated our capability to deliver with reliability and precision.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="msa-page__block">
      <h3 class="msa-page__title msa-page__title--center">Vendor excellence</h3>
      <p class="msa-page__subtitle msa-page__subtitle--center">Built on trust, performance and quality</p>
    </div>
    <div class="msa-page__cards grid grid-cols gap" style="--col-desktop: 3; --col-tablet: 2; --col-number: 1;">
      <div class="msa-page__card"><h4 class="msa-page__card-title">Vendor evaluation</h4><div class="msa-page__card-text rte"><p>At MSA, top priority is given to vendor evaluation, selection and training. We've developed a wide and competent vendor-base through relationships based on trust and performance.</p></div></div>
      <div class="msa-page__card"><h4 class="msa-page__card-title">Backup capacity</h4><div class="msa-page__card-text rte"><p>We maintain a second line of vendors prepared at all times for all running items, ensuring uninterrupted supply for our customers.</p></div></div>
      <div class="msa-page__card"><h4 class="msa-page__card-title">Quality assurance</h4><div class="msa-page__card-text rte"><p>We ensure all vendors meet strict quality and delivery requirements before being considered for an order, while helping promising vendors improve to global standards.</p></div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="msa-page__block">
      <h3 class="msa-page__title msa-page__title--center">Vendor certifications</h3>
      <ul class="msa-page__certs list-unstyled flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-15">
        <li class="msa-page__cert">Global Recycled Standard</li>
        <li class="msa-page__cert">Sedex</li>
        <li class="msa-page__cert">BSCI</li>
        <li class="msa-page__cert">C-TPAT</li>
        <li class="msa-page__cert">GOTS</li>
        <li class="msa-page__cert">ISO</li>
        <li class="msa-page__cert">WRAP</li>
        <li class="msa-page__cert">OEKO-TEX</li>
        <li class="msa-page__cert">BCI</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
